        DBForge installation


*** What you need ***
- OCaml 3.11 (or later) installed
- findlib
     http://projects.camlcity.org/projects/findlib.html
- Lablgtk2 >= 2.14.2 installed with findlib
     http://lablgtk.forge.ocamlcore.org/
- Config-file >= 1.1
     http://config-file.forge.ocamlcore.org/
- LablGtk-extras >= 1.1
     http://gtk-extras.forge.ocamlcore.org/
- OCaml-MySQL >= 1.0.4
     http://raevnos.pennmush.org/code/ocaml-mysql/
- Xml-light
     http://tech.motion-twin.com/xmllight.html
- make ;-)

*** How to compile ***
- ./configure
- make all
- make install

This will install the following findlib packages:
 dbforge, dbforge.gtk, dbforge.sql, dbforge.mysql and sqml

Executables (dbforge, dbforge-gtk) will be installed in
ocaml bin directory.
